-- Implemented in Phase 4. Empty-but-valid for now.
--
-- Design intent (CLAUDE.md §5): a `CovenantMonitor` contract readable need-to-know by the
-- agent bank / co-pilot party. The borrower's underlying financials are disclosed to the
-- agent bank and co-pilot only — never wholesale to lenders. The co-pilot reasons over this
-- private data and proposes a typed Daml choice; it can execute only what its party is
-- authorized to (see Syndicate.Roles.AgentAuthorization).
